      "review_summary": "The PR changes the cron agent tool default for omitted or invalid `runMode` from `force` to `due` and updates cron-tool expectations.\n\nPR surface: Source 0, Tests 0. Total 0 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source inspection: current main maps omitted agent-tool `runMode` to Gateway mode `force`, and force mode bypasses enabled and next-run checks in `isJobDue`. I did not run live tests in this read-only review.",
